div.p: Differences between sites per treatments outside and inside parakeet range for (a) mean total visits, and (b) the proportion of visits resulting in a feed (visits outside range n = 4027, inside range n = 6826). Black lines show controls and gray lines show treatments. Dotted lines denote differences between range sites within treatments which are not significant, solid lines are significant ( P values, * P < 0.05). Significant difference refers to differences within treatments between sites outside and inside the parakeet range.
